<br>
When Hippolyte was given back to the Amazons and became Queen, Yakut became a good friend of Hippolyte. <br>
<br>
Now, Yakut has family she knows nothing of, Her grandmother had more children than just Yakut's mother. So her blood line is long and rooted in Northern Amazon Lands.<br>
